<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>عِنْد ابْن سِيرِين،<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ لي:</span> يَا أَبَا صَالح.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٣٩٠٨ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو صَالح:</span> الْمُغيرَة بن حبيب،<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>ختن مَالك بن دِينَار <span class="c2">(ق ١٦٤ / ب)</span> .<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> حزم بن أبي حزم وكناه.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٣٩٠٩ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو صَالح:</span> غَالب بن سُلَيْمَان<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>الْبَصْرِيّ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> الضَّحَّاك بن مُزَاحم.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>أخبرنَا مُحَمَّد بن يُونُس، ثَنَا الْحُسَيْن بن مُحَمَّد<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> سَمِعت عَمْرو بن عَليّ،<span class="c5"> يَقُول:</span> غَالب<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>ابْن سُلَيْمَان الَّذِي يروي عَن الضَّحَّاك، يكنى<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>بِأبي صَالح.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>٣٩١٠ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو صَالح:</span> ابْن عَطِيَّة.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> شُعَيْب، قَالَه البُخَارِيّ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>٣٩١١ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو صَالح:</span> ذريح.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c5">روى حَدِيثه:</span> أهل فلسطين.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>سَمِعت مُحَمَّد بن يَعْقُوب،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> سَمِعت<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>عباسا،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> سَمِعت يحيى بن معِين، يَقُول<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>ذَلِك.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>٣٩١٢ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو صَالح:</span> اسْمه جُبَير.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> عَمْرو بن الْحَارِث.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>٣٩١٣ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو صَالح:</span> العطاردي.<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> يزِيد بن صَالح.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>ذكره البُخَارِيّ.<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>٣٩١٤ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو صَالح:</span> مولى عبد الله بن عَامر<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span>ابْن ربيعَة.<a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p26"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> عبد الله بن عَامر.<a href="#p26" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p27"></span>اُخْبُرْنَا عُثْمَان بن احْمَد السَّمرقَنْدِي بتنيس، ثَنَا<a href="#p27" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p28"></span>ابو أُميَّة مُحَمَّد بن ابراهيم، ثَنَا يَعْقُوب بن<a href="#p28" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p29"></span>مُحَمَّد الزُّهْرِيّ، ثَنَا مُحَمَّد بن فليح، حَدثنِي<a href="#p29" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p30"></span>أَبُو صَالح مولى عبد الله بن عَامر بن ربيعَة.<a href="#p30" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p31"></span>٣٩١٥ - أَبُو صَالح بكر بن خِدَاش.<a href="#p31" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p32"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> عِيسَى بن الْمسيب، وسُفْيَان<a href="#p32" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p33"></span>الثَّوْريّ.<a href="#p33" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p34"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> إِبْرَاهِيم بن يَعْقُوب الْجوزجَاني<a href="#p34" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p35"></span>وكناه.<a href="#p35" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p36"></span>٣٩١٦ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو صَالح:</span> أَحْمد بن ميسرَة.<a href="#p36" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p37"></span><span class="c5">روى عَن:</span> زِيَاد بن سعد.<a href="#p37" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p38"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> سُرَيج بن النُّعْمَان.<a href="#p38" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p39"></span>٣٩١٧ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو صَالح:</span> مَنْصُور بن <span class="c4">[صَالح]</span> .<a href="#p39" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p40"></span>قَالَه البُخَارِيّ.<a href="#p40" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p41"></span>٣٩١٨ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو صَالح:</span> إِسْحَاق بن نجيح<a href="#p41" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p42"></span>الْمَلْطِي.<a href="#p42" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p43"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> ابْن جريج.<a href="#p43" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p44"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> عَليّ بن حجر وكناه.<a href="#p44" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p45"></span>٣٩١٩ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو صَالح:</span> شُعَيْب بن حَرْب<a href="#p45" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p46"></span>الْمَدَائِنِي.<a href="#p46" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p47"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> الثَّوْريّ، وَشعْبَة.<a href="#p47" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>